# Exempt the dashboard's API-key management template directory
# (Slice 5). The root `keys/` pattern excludes crypto material that
# customers may leave next to the kit (Ed25519 pairs, etc.); the
# dashboard's `views/templates/keys/` subdir is unrelated source
# code and must ship in the repo.
!apps/dashboard/internal/views/templates/keys/
!apps/dashboard/internal/views/templates/keys/**
.DS_Store
